# Portfolio Rules (Cursor)

## Non-negotiables
- Dark-only UI. Preserve DYMO label vibe + grounded motion.
- Respect prefers-reduced-motion.
- Small diffs: touch the minimum files required.

## Two-world repo
- Next.js site = primary (ship here)
- legacy/design-inspo = reference (copy patterns from here, don’t invent new ones)

## Architecture discipline (Next.js)
- Keep copy in `src/data/**` (not scattered across components).
- Keep behavior isolated (no global state blobs).
- Keep styling token-driven; avoid one-off CSS.

## When porting from Design-Inspo
- Prefer “wrap then refactor”: mount the behavior first, then improve.
- Preserve DOM hooks/class naming if reusing CSS/JS behavior.
